Woh bakhsh ne waala maher-baan hai zindah nighebaan hai aur mai Uske huzoor taubah karta hu.", "Urdu": "بخشش کا طالب ہوں اﷲسے کہ جس کے سوا کوئی معبودنہیں وہ بخشنے والا مہربان ہے۔ زندہ نگہبان ہے اورمیں اس کے حضور توبہ کرتا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "AS-TAGH-FERUL-LAA-HAL LAZEE LAA ILAAHA ILLAA HOWAR RAHMAA-NUR RAHEE-MUL HAYYUL QAYYOOMO WA ATOOBO ILAIY-HE.", "ArabicText1": "اَسْتَغْفِرُ اللهَ الَّذِيْ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا هُوَ الرَّحْمٰنُ الرَّحِيْمُ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّوْمُ وَاَتُوْبُ اِلَيْهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012092, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "It is recommended to give alms (sadqah) in this month even if it is as small as a half date. It brings about rescue from Hellfire. Imam Sadiq (a) says; the reward for fasting in Sha’ban will be Paradise. Alms giving and imploring for forgiveness are the best deeds in Sha’ban. Verily, if anyone of you gives alms in Sha’ban, Almighty Allah will breed that alms in the very same way as you breed your small camels. Hence, this alms will be as huge as Mount Uhud on the Resurrection Day.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustahab hai keh is mahine mein sadqa de, agar-che woh aadha khajur hi kyu na ho, is se Khuda uske jism par Jahannam ki aag ko haraam kar dega. Imam Sadiq (a) farmate hai; Shaban mein roza rakhne ka sawaab Jannat hai. Mahe Shaban mein sadqa nikaalna aur isteghfaar karna behtareen amal hai. Yaqeenan, agar koi Mahe Shaban mein sadqa de, to Allah (swt) us sadqe ko roz-e-qayaamat Ohad ke baad ke maanind kar dega.", "UrduDescription": "صدقہ دے اگرچہ وہ نصف خرما ہی کیوں نہ ہو،اس سے خدا اس کے جسم پر جہنم کی آگ کو حرام کردے گا۔ امام جعفر صادق ؑسے ماہ ِرجب کے روزے کے بارے میں پوچھا گیا تو آپ نے فرمایا:تم ماہ ِشعبان کے روزے سے کیوں غافل ہو؟ راوی نے عرض کی : فرزندِ رسولؐ! شعبان کے ایک روزے کا ثواب کس قدر ہے؟ فرمایا :قسم بخدا!اس کااجر و ثواب بہشت ہے۔ اس نے عرض کی: اے فرزندِ رسولؐ! اس ماہ کا بہترین عمل کیا ہے؟ فرمایا : صدقہ و استغفار،جو شخص ماہِ شعبان میں صدقہ دے۔ تو خدا اس صدقے میں اس طرح بڑھاتا رہے گا جیسے تم لوگ اونٹنی کے بچے کو پال کر عظیم الجثہ[بھاری بھرکم] اونٹ بنا دیتے ہو چنانچہ یہ صدقہ قیامت کے روز احد کے پہاڑ کے مثل بڑھ کر اپنے مالک کے پاس آئے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "